    - target: {fileID: 1282522827012814712, guid: 8801e643e53a19d488f5168057473354,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '1. In Edit Mode, select the Pose Recorder GameObject and set the name
        of your pose. Also set the hand you would like to record with (left or right).


        2.
        In Play Mode, press the record button, make your desired pose and wait for
        the count down to record it.


        3. Recreate the pose with either hand.
        Each joint will turn green when in the correct rotation. You will be notified
        when the entire pose is detected.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
